				<p style="padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: #3687BF;">INCOME GENERATION:</span></strong>&nbsp;By empowering women with small business, tailoring, baking small scale farming skills.</p>
				<p style="padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: #3687BF;">SCHOOL SUPPORT: </span></strong>&nbsp;By donating 25% of income to the school feeding programme.</p>
				<p style="padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: #3687BF;">SUSTAINABILITY: </span></strong>&nbsp;By participating in opportunities that increase the sustainability of the group and the individuals within it.</p>


				<h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size:24px;">
