				</h2>

				<p>De’ Bridge community centre aims to increase the sustainability of its projects and to increase economic growth. The Women’s Empowerment group currently saves twenty percent of their income that goes back into this aim. Once enough capital has been raised, the group plans to lease land to start agricultural projects. This will further strengthen the community and enable the group to reach out to other women</p>
		
